        </header>
        <main class="px-3">
            <h1>OpenShop</h1>
            <p class="lead"> Welcome to OpenShop! <br> Jump right in and explore our many campgrounds. <br>
                Feel free to share some of your own and comment on others!</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn_about btn btn-lg font-weight-bold border-white bg-white">
                Start Shopping</a>
        </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2021</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</div>

